# 🏨 UniNest API Endpoint Table

| No | Module       | Method | Endpoint                                    | Access  | Description                             |
| -- | ------------ | ------ | ------------------------------------------- | ------- | --------------------------------------- |
| 1  | Auth         | POST   | `/api/auth/register`                        | Public  | Register a new user (student/admin)     |
| 2  | Auth         | POST   | `/api/auth/login`                           | Public  | Login and receive JWT token             |
| 3  | Hostels      | POST   | `/api/hostels`                              | Admin   | Create a new hostel                     |
| 4  | Hostels      | GET    | `/api/hostels`                              | Public  | View all hostels                        |
| 5  | Hostels      | GET    | `/api/hostels/:id`                          | Public  | View a single hostel                    |
| 6  | Hostels      | PUT    | `/api/hostels/:id`                          | Admin   | Update hostel details                   |
| 7  | Hostels      | DELETE | `/api/hostels/:id`                          | Admin   | Delete a hostel                         |
| 8  | Rooms        | POST   | `/api/rooms`                                | Admin   | Create a new room                       |
| 9  | Rooms        | GET    | `/api/rooms`                                | Public  | View all rooms                          |
| 10 | Rooms        | GET    | `/api/rooms/:id`                            | Public  | View a specific room                    |
| 11 | Rooms        | PUT    | `/api/rooms/:id`                            | Admin   | Update room details                     |
| 12 | Rooms        | DELETE | `/api/rooms/:id`                            | Admin   | Delete a room                           |
| 13 | Applications | POST   | `/api/applications`                         | Student | Apply for a hostel                      |
| 14 | Applications | GET    | `/api/applications`                         | Admin   | View all student applications           |
| 15 | Applications | GET    | `/api/applications/my`                      | Student | View own application                    |
| 16 | Allocations  | POST   | `/api/allocations`                          | Admin   | Allocate room to student                |
| 17 | Allocations  | GET    | `/api/allocations`                          | Admin   | View all room allocations               |
| 18 | Allocations  | GET    | `/api/allocations/my`                       | Student | View student’s room allocation          |
| 19 | Allocations  | PUT    | `/api/allocations/request-cancellation`     | Student | Request cancellation of room allocation |
| 20 | Allocations  | PUT    | `/api/allocations/approve-cancellation/:id` | Admin   | Approve cancellation request            |
| 21 | Allocations  | DELETE | `/api/allocations/:id`                      | Admin   | Cancel allocation manually              |

